graph TB
    subgraph "CodeFlare Operator"
        Manager[Manager Deployment]
        RayController[RayCluster Controller]
        AppController[AppWrapper Controller<br/>Optional]
        RayWebhook[RayCluster Webhook]
        AppWebhook[AppWrapper Webhook]
        MetricsServer[Metrics Server<br/>:8080]
        HealthProbes[Health Probes<br/>:8081]
        CertController[Certificate Controller]

        Manager --> RayController
        Manager --> AppController
        Manager --> RayWebhook
        Manager --> AppWebhook
        Manager --> MetricsServer
        Manager --> HealthProbes
        Manager --> CertController
    end

    User[User/SDK] -->|creates| RayClusterCR[RayCluster CR]
    User -->|creates| AppWrapperCR[AppWrapper CR]

    RayClusterCR -->|webhook| RayWebhook
    AppWrapperCR -->|webhook| AppWebhook

    RayWebhook -->|validates/mutates| RayClusterCR
    AppWebhook -->|validates/mutates| AppWrapperCR

    RayClusterCR -->|watched by| RayController
    AppWrapperCR -->|watched by| AppController

    RayController -->|creates| CASecret[CA Secret<br/>mTLS certificates]
    RayController -->|creates| TLSSecret[TLS Secret<br/>node certificates]
    RayController -->|creates| OAuthSecret[OAuth Config<br/>dashboard auth]
    RayController -->|creates| HeadService[RayCluster Head Service<br/>8443/TCP, 10001/TCP]
    RayController -->|creates| Ingress[Ingress/Route<br/>external access]
    RayController -->|creates| NetworkPolicy[Network Policies<br/>pod isolation]

    AppController -->|creates| KueueWorkload[Kueue Workload CR]
    AppController -->|manages| WrappedResources[Wrapped Resources<br/>RayCluster, etc.]

    CertController -->|manages| WebhookCert[Webhook TLS Cert<br/>auto-rotation]

    %% External Dependencies
    RayController -->|watches| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]
    AppController -->|integrates| Kueue[Kueue Scheduler]
    RayController -->|reads| DSCInit[DSCInitialization CR]

    MetricsServer -->|scraped by| Prometheus[Prometheus]

    %% Styling
    style Manager fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style RayController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style AppController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style RayWebhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style AppWebhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style RayClusterCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style AppWrapperCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style KubeRay fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Kueue fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style DSCInit fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333
